idHookRunner struct {\\n    RepoDir string\\n    T       TestT  // same interface as HookRunner.T\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThe `runFactoryDroidHookInRepoDir` method should execute:\\n```\\nexec.Command(getTestBinary(), \\\"hooks\\\", \\\"factoryai-droid\\\", hookName)\\n```\\nwith `cmd.Dir = r.RepoDir`, `cmd.Stdin = bytes.NewReader(inputJSON)`, and `cmd.Env = os.Environ()` (no special project dir env var needed).\\n\\n**Hook simulation methods on `FactoryDroidHookRunner`:**\\n\\n- `SimulateUserPromptSubmit(sessionID string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"test prompt\\\"}`\\n- `SimulateStop(sessionID, transcriptPath string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"...\\\"}`\\n- `SimulateSessionStart(sessionID string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"\\\"}`\\n- `SimulateSessionEnd(sessionID, transcriptPath string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"...\\\"}`\\n- `SimulatePreTask(sessionID, transcriptPath, toolUseID string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"tool_use_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"tool_input\\\":{}}`\\n- `SimulatePostTask(input PostTaskInput) error` -- sends full post-task input with `tool_response.agentId`\\n- `SimulatePreCompact(sessionID, transcriptPath string) error` -- sends `{\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"transcript_path\\\":\\\"...\\\"}`\\n\\n**Output variants:**\\n- `SimulateUserPromptSubmitWithOutput(sessionID string) HookOutput`\\n- `SimulateSessionStartWithOutput(sessionID string) HookOutput`\\n\\n**FactoryDroidSession struct:**\\n\\n```go\\ntype FactoryDroidSession struct {\\n    ID             string\\n    TranscriptPath string\\n    env            *TestEnv\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**`NewFactoryDroidSession()` on TestEnv** -- creates a session with a `.jsonl` transcript path in `.entire/tmp/`, incrementing `SessionCounte